features: Our durable and long-lasting 100 GSM mesh-reinforced clear tarpaulins are available in a wide range of small, medium, large and extra-large sizes. Covers protect your objects and surfaces against damage from rain, snow, frost, wind and dust, indoors and outdoors.
Our transparent polyethylene tarpaulins are an ideal choice for covering cars, vans, bikes, trailers, boats, shelters, agricultural materials, firewood, log stores, furniture, and garden pools.
They are also perfect as transparent roofing sheets, tent groundsheets, pond covers, awning sheets, chicken run covers, rabbit run covers, and balcony rain protection.

The edges of the tarpaulin are finished with reinforced bounds. The corners are reinforced with rubber that enables you to firmly attach the tarp with tarpaulin fixings (fixings not included). Around the whole circumference of the protective cover are aluminium fixing eyelets (every about 100 cm). Our tarpaulins are waterproof, mould-resistant, easy to wash, and UV-stabilized which prevents go yellowish.

The product is made of polyethylene, which makes it extremely durable and retains its functional properties. Please note: The supplier has the right in his policy during the production of his tarpaulin to make it +10% as -10% big.
